metadata.name: BFC VIP #1
metadata.description: Bored Founders Club (BFC) is a global community of tech, startup and web3 enthusiasts. Developers, founders, creators, investors and more. Together we're building the most influential tech, startup and web3 community in the world. BFC VIP NFT is the second most valuable piece in the BFC ecosystem (only 2500 NFTs). It gives you VIP access to the Bored Founders Club. Build the future of the web with us. Visit www.BoredFoundersClub.com for more details.
